[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "……劣勢。ここまでの力を出してくるとは。\n姉上たちの本気を体感",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_00062",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "生憎、こっちも強くならなきゃいけなくてね。\nあの海を越えるためにも……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00063",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ヤド姉……ダメ……ヤだよ。\nこのままじゃ、負けて大ケガしちゃうよ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00064",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うっ……！\nなに、この感じ……ゾワゾワする！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00065",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "まずい！　キューンがキレる！\nみんな、気を付けるんだ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00066",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なになに！？\nいったいどういうことよ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00067",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "いい加減に……してーーー！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00068",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ああなったキューンは手が付けられない……\n泣く子は強いってことさね！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00069",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "くうっ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00070",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なっ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00071",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "いやいやいや……嘘っすよね？\n強すぎませんこれ？　あ、ヤバ……体が震えて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00072",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "末っ子だからね、培ってきた色々な技術が\n詰め込まれてるのさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00073",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "予定を変更、状況を利用し、キューンを援護する",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_00074",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ふ……到着早々、派手な出迎えだな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00075",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "えっ？　この声は――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00076",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "はぁっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00077",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "っ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00078",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "ティム！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00079",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "今だっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00080",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あうっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00081",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "キューン！！\n……獣人の新手！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_00082",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ジェロンさん！　それにティムくんまで！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00083",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "間に合ってよかった。\nようやくレスナさんに恩返しができるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00084",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "どうやらレスナの知り合いみたいだね？\n思わぬ援軍、ありがたいこった！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00085",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "……作戦の続行は不能。今回は撤退する",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_00086",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "……行ってくれたか。\nキレたキューン相手じゃ分が悪かったから、助かったよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00087",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "不意を打てただけだ。\n次も上手くいく保証はない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00088",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ジェロンさん、お久しぶりです！\nティムくんは外に出て大丈夫なんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00089",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "はい。レスナさんやアーシャさんの薬のおかげで、\nもうすっかり元気になりました！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00090",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "まだまだ目は離せんがな。\n閉じこもっていた分、外の世界を見せてやりたいんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00091",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あ、あの……はじめまして、\nレスナのお友達ですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00092",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "友達、か……ああ、そうだな。\nジェロン・ディーゼルだ。王国騎士の支援をしている",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00093",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "弟のティム・ディーゼルです。\nよろしくお願いします！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00094",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ジェロン……って、前にレスナが言ってた……！　\nど、ども、よろしくっす",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00095",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "怯える必要はない。暴れていたのは昔の話だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00096",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "それもティムの病を治すためだった。\nレスナが弟を治してくれた以上、暴れる理由も消えた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00097",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "レスナちゃんの薬のおかげかな？　ティム君、\n獣人のアタシから見てもすっごく素早かったよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00098",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "いや、生来の力に違いない。\nうちのティムは控えめに言って天才だからな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00099",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あ、あはは、大層な弟想いのお兄様のようで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00100",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "うちの姉様も天才だから。優れ者だと国中騒ぐから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_00101",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "対抗せんでよろしいが、その心意気やよしでもある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00102",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あの……イェルカさん！　ありがとうございます。\nイェルカさんのお言葉、嬉しかったです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00103",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "まあ、ね。子どものケンカに親が出るようなやり方は\n野暮ってもんだろ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00104",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "なんにせよ、これで完全にヤドヴィガ……というか\nアウグストに敵対しちまったのは確かだし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00105",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "これからは心置きなく、全力で\nレスナたちを守ってやるさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00106",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "えーと、とりあえずはイェルカに同じってことで",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00107",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "いや、シトリンは信用できないから。\nなんじゃい、とりあえずって。舐めとるんか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00108",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "僕はレスナたちを観察したいんだよ。\nそれを邪魔するなら戦うさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00109",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "だから信用ならないっての……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00110",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 49,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "邪魔が入ったけど、それじゃあ予定通り\nブラオールに出発ってことでいい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00111",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 50,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "船に余裕があれば俺とティムも連れていってくれ。\nレスナの役に立とうとここまで来たのだからな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00112",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 51,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ノーヴァ神聖国は港に入っただけで終わりかぁ。\n　ちょっと残念。また観光したかったな）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00113",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 52,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "むっ！？　ティム、観光したかったという顔だな。\nならば観光していこうか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00114",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 53,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "だ、大丈夫だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00115",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 54,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "また今度ね。そのときはアタシがしっかり\n神聖国を案内してあげるから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00116",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 55,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "九偉人がクリセルダを狙ってる件は\n後で殿下やブラッドさんに伝えとくね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00117",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 56,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ、そうだね。直接王国のほうに行くかもしれないし\n警備を強化してもらわないと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00118",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 57,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "クリセルダなら大抵の追手は返り討ちだろうが、\nあの強さだ。油断はできんな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00119",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 58,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "んじゃ、諸々の準備を整えまして……\nいきやすか、ブラオールに！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00120",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 59,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン・ディーゼル",
		"romanized_name": "Geron Diezel",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "身体の一部が獣化した錬金術士。元「極夜の錬金党」。\n現在は弟のティムと共に、王国騎士団に協力している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 60,
		"localized_name": "ティム・ディーゼル",
		"romanized_name": "Tim Diezel",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "身体の一部が獣化した少年。ジェロンの弟。\n現在はジェロンと共に、王国騎士団に協力している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]